<p begin="00:00:48.015" end="00:00:52.786" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">MY STUDIO TONIGHT, YOU MAY VERY </span><span style="block">WELL BE HUNTED FOR SPORT.</span></p>

