<p begin="00:01:42.603" end="00:01:48.208" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; WE GO TO WHERE THE REPORTS OF </span><span style="block">CRIME ARE.</span></p>

<p begin="00:01:48.208" end="00:01:55.983" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">THOSE UNFORTUNATELY HAPPEN TO BE </span><span style="block">POOR NEIGHBORHOODS AND MY  *R </span><span style="block">MINORITY NEIGHBORHOOD.</span></p>


<p begin="00:01:55.983" end="00:02:00.254" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Stephen: OKAY, THE PROGRAM </span><span style="block">IS NOT ABOUT COLOR, IT'S ABOUT </span><span style="block">FRISKABILITY.</span></p>


<p begin="00:02:00.254" end="00:02:02.823" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">(LAUGHTER) </span><span style="block">IN FACT, I DON'T SEE COLOR, NOT </span><span style="block">EVEN MY OWN.</span></p>


<p begin="00:02:02.823" end="00:02:10.063" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">PEOPLE TELL ME I'M WHITE AND I </span><span style="block">BELIEVE THEM BECAUSE I DON'T GET </span><span style="block">FRISKED.</span></p>


<p begin="00:02:10.063" end="00:02:17.938" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">(LAUGHTER) </span><span style="block">THE POINT IS FOR YEARS, FOR </span><span style="block">YEARS THIS HAS BEEN A SAFE CITY, </span><span style="block">A WONDERFUL TOY FOR A GIRL AND A </span><span style="block">BOY.</span></p>




<p begin="00:02:17.938" end="00:02:24.111" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">BUT NOW IT WILL BE TEEMING WITH </span><span style="block">UNFRISKED BLACK AND/OR HISPANIC </span><span style="block">PEOPLE.</span></p>


<p begin="00:02:24.111" end="00:02:28.315" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">I WON'T PWEFPB ABLE TO CROSS THE </span><span style="block">STREET TO AVOID A SUSPICIOUS </span><span style="block">LOOKING AFRICAN AMERICAN WITHOUT</span></p>


