<p begin="00:02:31.818" end="00:02:37.724" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">WHICH MEANS I HAVE TO WALK DOWN </span><span style="block">THE MIDDLE OF THE STREET "HERE </span><span style="block">COMES THE CAB" I'M DEAD.</span></p>


<p begin="00:02:37.724" end="00:02:46.834" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">(LAUGHTER) </span><span style="block">AND, FOLKS, IT'S NOT JUST WHO'S </span><span style="block">ON THE STREETS NOW, IT'S ALSO </span><span style="block">ABOUT THE THUGS HEADED BACK </span><span style="block">THERE.</span></p>




