<p begin="00:03:13.360" end="00:03:19.099" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">IT'S LIKE EVERY MINOR DRUG </span><span style="block">OFFENDER SUDDENLY BECAME A WHITE </span><span style="block">COLLEGE STUDENT.</span></p>


