<p begin="00:03:59.606" end="00:04:05.078" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; THEY'RE NOW EXPANDING INTO </span><span style="block">SPORTING EVENTS, RODEOS, MUSIC </span><span style="block">FESTIVALS.</span></p>


