<p begin="00:04:59.733" end="00:05:03.871" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">JUST LIKE IF YOU EVER CHEAT ON </span><span style="block">YOUR GIRLFRIEND YOU HAVE TO GET </span><span style="block">A BUNCH MORE GIRLFRIEND SO</span></p>


