<p begin="00:05:49.316" end="00:05:55.289" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">(LAUGHTER) </span><span style="block">IT'S THE ONLY WAY TO MAKE SURE </span><span style="block">EVERYONE'S SAFE BEFORE THEY </span><span style="block">CRASH FOR OUR AMUSEMENT.</span></p>



