<p begin="00:06:49.076" end="00:06:52.980" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">MR. PINKER, THANKS FOR COMING </span><span style="block">BACK.</span></p>

<p begin="00:06:52.980" end="00:07:01.622" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">(CHEERS AND APPLAUSE) </span><span style="block">THE BOOK IS CALLED "THE BETTER </span><span style="block">ANGELS OF OUR NATURE: WHY </span><span style="block">VIOLENCE HAS DECLINED."</span></p>



